  "description": "<h3>Back of Case - Atari ST (UK) (from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/formula-1-grand-prix/adblurbs\">Ad Blurbs</a>)</h3>Experience the thrills and spills of Formula 1 Racing, whether you own an older banger, a Porsche Turbo or are too young to drive, you too will enjoy the challenge of competing on the track. Choose from one of the five powerful Turbo charged racers, all set up with different handling and performance characteristics to compete against the best drivers in the world over the six Championship Circuits:<br>\nThe game features:<br>\n<b>SIX FAMOUS CIRCUITS &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; FIVE CARS OF DIFFERING PERFORMANCES &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; SIX SPEED GEARBOXES &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ENGINE REV. LIMITS &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; TIMED PRACTICE LABS FOR GRID POSITION &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; UP TO THREE CARS ON THE TRACK AT THE SAME TIME &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; ONE RACE OR CHAMPIONSHIP SERIES &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; LAP RECORDS &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; CIRCUIT RECORDS &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; WORLD CHAMPIONSHIPS<br>\nA superb race game no 16 Bit owner should be without - the ultimate driving experience.</b>",
